N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 65.9 - Returns

State Regulations

No merchandise shall be accepted for return from a
retailer except pursuant to a court order, or with approval by the Liquor

Authority, for good cause shown. Notes
